experience with BPMN influences how much they can benefit
from assistance. To this end we split the data into two groups
— experts, which we define for the purposes of this analysis
as participants with at least one year
of BPMN modeling experience, and novices, which are the
remaining study participants.
This split results in 10 experts and 18 novices.
